What is VRM? In the past, when trying to handle the 3D humanoid avatar (3D model) in Virtual Reality, Virtual YouTuber, etc., it was necessary to develop an unique system for applications and fine-tune the 3D model data due to&hellip;
 The output data is depend on how creators make the 3D model and what modeling tools are used
 The coordinate system is different. The scale is different. The initial pose is different.
